<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Complete your <%= Customer.name_label %> Driver Conduct Agreement</h1>

    <p>
      Please complete the <%= link_to "driver conduct agreement", url_for(host: (Customer.current_customer.url_shortcut + "." + ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host]), controller: 'mentor_signup', action: 'driver_form', only_path: false) %> to confirm your status as a driver
      for <%= Customer.name_label %>. You will not be able to drive until you have done so.
    </p>

    <p class="footer">
      Sent to you by DreamSIS. You are receiving this message because you have been marked as a driver by a
      <%= Customer.name_label %> representative.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
